msg: Upgrade from Ant 1.8.4 to Ant 1.9.0: in the process I have also switched the naming convention of jars to the new one we are adopting for example for Tomcat jars that is <NAME-OF-THE-EXTERNAL-PROJECT>-<RELEASE-NUMBER>-<ORIGINAL-NAME-OF-JAR-FILE>.
For example, in in the release package apache-ant-1.9.0.zip we have the jar ant-launcher.jar, the name of the jar in OFBiz is: ant-1.9.0-ant-launcher.jar
